One implementation note for the devs

The existing spec has order numbering as ORD-1234 with invoice numbering INV-1234-01, INV-1234-02 etc. With this model, you'd have e.g. INV-1234-01 (Deposit) and INV-1234-02 (Balance) coexisting and both posting to Xero independently. Confirm with Ariane that Xero is happy receiving two invoices with sequential numbers tied to the same order — it should be fine, but worth checking her Xero workflow.

This model is genuinely elegant once you see it: deposits, supplementary invoices, and standard invoices are all the same thing — claims for portions of an order total. One unified concept replaces three special cases.

